nk="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-24/ty-article/u-s-deploys-more-arms-and-troops-to-israel-cyprus-and-jordan/0000018b-5cbf-d307-adbb-7dbf1aa80000</guid></item><item><title>在黎巴嫩，平民听到以色列的战争威胁，但无处可逃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/in-lebanon-civilians-hear-israeli-threats-of-war-but-have-nowhere-to-turn/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff3622b20000</link><description>对于因预期以色列和真主党之间的冲突升级而逃离黎巴嫩南部的平民来说，贝鲁特缺乏正常运作的政府使生活变得更加困难</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/in-lebanon-civilians-hear-israeli-threats-of-war-but-have-nowhere-to-turn/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff3622b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙地面进攻之前进行了一场令人紧张的等待游戏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</link><description>加沙地面行动的拖延加剧了政府与军队之间以及政府内部的信任危机 ■ 在释放两名以色列老年妇女后，哈马斯希望部分释放人质能够减轻其面临的国际压力在下面</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Oct 2023 03:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-24/ty-article/.premium/israel-plays-a-nerve-wracking-waiting-game-ahead-of-a-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018b-5e32-d8e2-a1eb-ff36c1350000</guid></item><item><title>“安德森·库珀说：我有一段关于你被绑架儿子的视频”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 22:14:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2023-10-24/ty-article-podcast/anderson-cooper-said-i-have-a-video-of-your-kidnapped-son/0000018b-5e1a-d8e2-a1eb-ff1e67b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的首要任务必须是释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-10-24/ty-article-op