icle/.premium/officials-close-to-pm-call-for-delay-of-gaza-ground-op-social-media-campaign-follows-suit/0000018b-5d5f-d8e2-a1eb-ff5fc8390000</link><description>政治消息来源质疑这些信息的传播是否表明内塔尼亚胡正在试图为推迟甚至避免在加沙地带进行大规模地面行动做好舆论准备</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 18:30:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/officials-close-to-pm-call-for-delay-of-gaza-ground-op-social-media-campaign-follows-suit/0000018b-5d5f-d8e2-a1eb-ff5fc8390000</guid></item><item><title>国际刑事法院将于 2024 年 2 月就以色列在巴勒斯坦领土上的行为的后果举行听证会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-hold-hearings-on-consequences-of-israeli-practices-in-palestinian-territory/0000018b-5d70-d8e2-a1eb-ff7690810000</link><description>国际法院将于明年二月举行听证会，要求就包括东耶路撒冷在内的被占领土上的做法的法律影响提供咨询意见</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 17:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/world-court-to-hold-hearings-on-consequences-of-israeli-practices-in-palestinian-territory/0000018b-5d70-d8e2-a1eb-ff7690810000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最需要帮助的时刻，内塔尼亚胡的右翼民粹主义朋友去了哪里？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-23/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-hour-of-need-where-did-netanyahus-right-wing-populist-friends-go/0000018b-5d56-d8e2-a1eb-ff56076d0000</link><description>除了以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡令人震惊的一长串政治和概念失败之外，还要加上他对世界各地极右翼盟友深不可测、短视的信任</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 17:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-23/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-hour-of-need-where-did-netanyahus-right-wing-populist-friends-go/0000018b-5d56-d8e2-a1eb-ff56076d0000</guid></item><item><title>我们应该将哈马斯的袭击与大屠杀进行比较吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/should-we-compare-the-hamas-assault-to-the-holocaust/0000018b-5cbb-d307-adbb-7dbb40b50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:21:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/should-we-compare-the-hamas-assault-to-the-holocaust/0000018b-5cbb-d307-adbb-7dbb40b50000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列加沙战争的支持是否会让他输掉 2024 年大选？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-bidens-support-of-israels-gaza-war-cost-him-the-2024-election/0000018b-5c62-d2b2-addf-7e7a1d6e0000</link><description>摇摆州的阿拉伯和穆斯林社区威胁不在明年的总统选举中投票给乔·拜登，巴勒斯坦裔美国众议员拉希达·特莱布带头谴责</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/could-bidens-support-of-israels-gaza-war-cost-him-the-2024-election/0000018b-5c62-d2b2-addf-7e7a1d6e0000</guid></item><item><title>这位以色列教授警告犹太父母不要让他们的孩子进入美国精英大学</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-professor-is-warning-jewish-parents-to-keep-their-kids-away-from-elite-u-s-colleges/0000018b-5c37-d8e2-a1eb-ff37fcba0000</link><description>哈马斯袭击以色列后，哥伦比亚大学的 Shai Davidai 教授公开表达了美国学术机构的安全担忧。他指责自己的大学校长未能打击校园内支持恐怖分子的学生组织</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 14:00:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-professor-is-warning-jewish-parents-to-keep-their-kids-away-from-elite-u-s-colleges/0000018b-5c37-d8e2-a1eb-ff37fcba0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀之后，创伤治疗将不再一样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dealing-with-national-trauma-after-hamas-attack-classic-psychotherapy-is-not-enough/0000018b-3e23-df22-a5eb-3f7b14f20000</link><description>哈马斯的突然袭击让以色列震惊不已。当事件正在进行并且现实感觉不安全时，治疗创伤的传统方法是不够的，但以色列人以同情心对待彼此肯定会有所帮助</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 13:43:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dealing-with-national-trauma-after-hamas-attack-classic-psychotherapy-is-not-enough/0000018b-3e23-df22-a5eb-3f7b14f20000</guid></item><item><title>歌手公开反对哈马斯大屠杀后，麦当娜的安保细节得到升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/madonnas-security-detail-upgraded-after-singer-speaks-out-against-hamas-massacre/0000018b-5c70-d00f-a9bf-7c78761b0000</link><description>这位已经开始全球庆祝巡演的歌手谴责了这起致命袭击，并写道“我的心与以色列同在”，她在社交媒体上受到了严厉的批评。</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/madonnas-security-detail-upgraded-after-singer-speaks-out-against-hamas-massacre/0000018b-5c70-d00f-a9bf-7c78761b0000</guid></item><item><title>破坏者成功地将特拉维夫从地图上抹去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/saboteurs-successfully-erase-tel-aviv-off-the-maps/0000018b-5b9d-d473-a5fb-7fdd33210000</link><description>OpenStreetMap 曾出现过编辑战争，用户反复恢复地图上已删除的部分，并阻止正在删除它们的用户。自第一次删除以来，已有数十次编辑和重建</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:20:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/saboteurs-successfully-erase-tel-aviv-off-the-maps/0000018b-5b9d-d473-a5fb-7fdd33210000</guid></item><item><title>在反犹太主义抬头之际，英国犹太人为在加沙被扣押的以色列人质举行集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</link><description>反犹太主义袭击增加了 1,350% 以上，犹太教堂和犹太学校加强了安全措施，但这并没有阻止英国犹太人周日大批参加伦敦特拉法加广场的示威活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Oct 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-10-23/ty-article/.premium/british-jews-rally-for-israeli-hostages-held-in-gaza-amid-rising-antisemitism/0000018b-5c31-d8e2-a1eb-ff37966a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>